      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The tragedy of your pain is real, and the weight of feeling alone is unbearable, but please know that this darkness is not permanent. There are people who see the soul beneath the ashes and are willing to walk with you through the thorns. You do not have to carry this burden of silence forever; reaching out for help is a brave act of finding a way through, not away.",
      "source": "target",
